article:
This is a 'list of the 100 busiest airports in the [[Nordic countries]]' by
passengers per year, aircraft movements per year and freight & mail tonnes per
year for 2012, 2011 and 2010.

The list also includes yearly statistics for the busiest metropolitan airport
systems for 2012 and the busiest air-routes for 2011 and 2010 (will be expanded
for 2012 as soon as the statistics is made available).

A link to older statistics for 2006â2009 is provided below.

Airports in Greenland are until further notice not included due to lack of
officially published data from the Greenland Airport Authority and/or Statistics
Greenland.

This transport-related list is intended to be regularly updated as new
statistics becomes available from the relevant official authorities.
